sys_update_xml.name: sys_ui_section_7dadfa08c3901200378f587981d3ae76
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update><sys_ui_section caption="" section_id="7dadfa08c3901200378f587981d3ae76" sys_domain="global" table="em_alert_correlation_rule" version="3" view=""><sys_ui_annotation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><is_plain_text>false</is_plain_text><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-02-15 09:36:30</sys_created_on><sys_id>13601e8493013200a346f179077ffbbb</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-02-15 09:36:30</sys_updated_on><text><p>The rule will run only for new alerts or alerts whose status changed from close/flapping to open/reopen.</p>

<p><b>Primary alert:</b> An alert that matches this filter is the representative of it's correlated alerts. To see the correlated alert under it, double click the alert in the alert console.</p>

<p><b>Secondary alert:</b> An alert that matches this filter is not shown in the alert console.</p>

<p><b>Advanced:</b> A state change on an alert that matches the Filter will start the rule. The rule will create correlation primary and secondary connections from the alert according to the Script result.</p>

<br></br>

<p><b>Relationship type:</b> </p>

<p><b>No Relationship-</b> Ignore the relationship when looking for a match.</p>

<p><b>Same CI or Node-</b> Both alerts need to be related with the same CI. If the CI field is blank, then the alerts need to have the same Node value.</p>

<p><b>Primary is Parent-</b> The relationship is in the direction of parent (primary) to child as described in the CI Relationship Types table.</p>

<p><b>Primary is Child-</b> The relationship is in the opposite direction, child (primary) to parent.</p>

<br></br>

<p><b>Time Difference In Minutes:</b> </p><p>

The alerts considered are only those that arrive within this time window (determined by "Last event generation time" field on the alert).</p></text><type display_value="Info Box
